{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2300246, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "现在就是毫无隔离地面对现世的痛苦，但又没有充分的理由和胆量去死", "timestamp": 1629209306, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300271, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "感受生活的痛苦与快乐，才能真正感到活着", "timestamp": 1629209549, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300275, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "slw，沉浸在抑郁中到一定程度反而对一切都不太在意，平静地向往着死亡，而从这种状态脱离重新开始生活时，因为期待又反而产生了更多精神的矛盾与痛苦", "timestamp": 1629209572, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300279, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以陌生人，请你不要逃避痛苦。不要逃避生命的礼物。要珍惜感受一切的能力", "timestamp": 1629209598, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300280, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "美好与丑恶并存，痛苦与快乐并存", "timestamp": 1629209634, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300283, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": 2300275, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 是啊…那时候一切都不是很真切，是持续低落黯淡想解脱的状态。现在好了有种冰层融化的感觉，反而对世间真切的苦痛更敏感了，就想重新冰封自己", "timestamp": 1629209644, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300284, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": 2300279, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 谢谢你", "timestamp": 1629209648, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300285, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "来这个世界一趟不容易，好好体会一切是难得的力量", "timestamp": 1629209668, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300336, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "唉，我都怀疑我的抑郁能不能好，还怀疑会不会是双相", "timestamp": 1629210242, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300341, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": 2300336, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 摸摸头，好好吃药好好看医生会好的，虽然会很久，dz也和它对抗了三年", "timestamp": 1629210288, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2300360, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": 2300341, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我假期也老胸闷不舒服，想换药又怕副作用，因为过渡期要在学校度过怕不能上课", "timestamp": 1629210470, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301009, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "怎么判断是否好了，是不是做心理测试题（我猜的，纯好奇）", "timestamp": 1629214937, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301026, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "摸摸dz 我没有抑郁症经常这样想 觉得活着不值得但又没勇气去死 不过吃好吃的还是能让我振作起来", "timestamp": 1629215062, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2302315, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": 2301009, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 情绪、感知力、行动力上都有很大区别，就是我说的那种冰层解冻的感觉，你会重新变得鲜活，能用合理的时间完成工作。如果之前有躯体化症状的话，症状显著减轻趋于没有，那就是差不多了", "timestamp": 1629248709, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2302317, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": 2301009, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 其实是应该重新去医院的，但我没有，我擅自停药了，这点不要学😂不过我确实自信自己好了，就不是很想再去医院", "timestamp": 1629248750, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2302319, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": 2301026, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 也摸摸你！", "timestamp": 1629248785, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2331090, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 2240, "w": 1080}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": 2300336, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 有怀疑可以复诊问问医生！医生不会嫌烦的！双相和抑郁用药还挺不一样的最好看看清楚。", "timestamp": 1629568826, "type": "image", "url": "bl/blrbzpdhlzckskqmcby5li3q3z56mq4h.jpeg"}, {"cid": 2332168, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": 2331090, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 感谢！", "timestamp": 1629603806, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2472788, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 974, "w": 752}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 441728, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1631248393, "type": "image", "url": "gy/gy2gi5erkcioi5jczm7dwley35qlwhep.png"}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 10, "pid": 441728, "reply": 19, "tag": null, "text": "抑郁症治好以后竟然有点想回到抑郁症时期，沉浸于疾病带来的痛苦而忽视了现实生活中的很多事，某种意义上也是一种难得的逃避。如果继续不干预可能还会逃向死亡，也能有充分的理由早点离开这个可怖的世界，不用经历一些更黑暗的事。有点后悔主动寻求治疗了", "timestamp": 1629209164, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1631248393, "url": "", "vote": {}}}